WE'RE USING HIM AS A TOOL,

19:41.413 --> 19:45.849
JUST LIKE ANY OTHER TOOL
IN OUR ARSENAL.

19:45.884 --> 19:49.220
ANYTHING THAT CAN HELP US
GET A CLEARER PICTURE.

19:49.255 --> 19:50.654
I KNOW NOTHING,

19:50.689 --> 19:52.290
