COMPLETELY YET.

20:49.449 --> 20:52.582
BUT JUST SO YOU KNOW...

20:52.617 --> 20:54.619
YOU'VE GOT
TWO THINGS HERE.

20:54.654 --> 20:55.652
OKAY.

20:55.687 --> 20:56.920
