21:35.294 --> 21:37.328
OKAY.

21:42.266 --> 21:43.635
THAT'S THE CONNECTION
TO YOU.

21:53.712 --> 21:56.247
SOMEWHERE, SOMEHOW,
THERE'S A STORY OF CHILD ABUSE.

