THROUGH TO YOU.

23:26.839 --> 23:28.238
I'LL BET YOU ANYTHING.

23:28.273 --> 23:31.042
DO YOUR --
DO THE THINGS THAT YOU DO BEST.

23:31.077 --> 23:33.176
